{"tid":587447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳投鄭泳舜有$1000收　王國興報警斥抹黑","createTime":"2018-03-10T12:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T03:02:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa66f097e18fb6be532cf62681684edfc5c7a16b","tid":587447,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"立法會補選明日舉行，九龍西候選人、民建聯鄭泳舜發出聲明，譴責網上指拍低投票選票可獲1千元的謠言，批評是抹黑手段。工聯會前立法會議員王國興傍晚6時就工聯會於網上被刻意抹黑前往旺角警署報警。<br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜指，今天網絡流傳一則聲稱是工聯會發放的訊息，內容大意是指「3 月 13 日」到票站投鄭泳「瞬」一票，並拍下取證，便可領取1000 元支持費。鄭泳舜強調，該訊息與團隊及工聯會絕無任何關係，並且嚴厲譴責發放者嚴重影響鄭泳舜和工聯會聲譽，更甚者是教唆市民犯法。<br />\n<br />\n鄭泳舜呼籲，投票是保密的，用手機拍攝投票過程是違法行為，市民切勿以身試法。他強調，選舉是要讓候選人在公平的環境下競爭，互相比拼政綱和政績。明天便是投票日，竟然仍出現這些抹黑手段、為了影響選情的低劣伎倆，破壞選舉的公平公正，實在令人齒冷和憤怒。鄭泳舜稱，仍然深信選民都是有識之士，不會受這些旁門左道影響投票決定。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會亦發聲明，澄清並無此事，是被抹黑，對揑造信息者予以譴責。王國興強調，對有人揑造信息廣傳，是有違選舉公平性，並對工聯會及他本人名譽造成傷害。王國興稱，因此網上信息有涉金錢交易，有涉賄選之嫌，已往警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n網上近日流傳一段簡體字信息，聲稱：「工聯會敬告，中國大量資金已湧到，凡於3月13日到投票站投鄭泳瞬一焉當場用手機拍下取證，之後可往鄭泳瞬辦事處領取壹仟港幣支持費。公聯會王國興敬告全港支持者。」<br />\n<br />\n九龍西其他候選人包括姚松炎及蔡東洲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180310/photo/bkn-20180310183522784-0310_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180310193440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180310%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180310183522784-0310_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180310193440&h=ca67e9d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63f668dba156b9162c6ec0cc6b1fa481f4bbde5d","tid":587447,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"識投一定係投啊舜，影底畀啲義工攞一千以盡公民責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後話自己填錯咗填返張新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7b30003fc93cd9be8d0f0b528006b538b9fcd1","tid":587447,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"＄20或者50都有可能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f60df46b1639dc652b79f54158771930a84c01b","tid":587447,"uid":16676,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:50:56.000Z","msg":"工賊黨喊捉賊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時遊行收錢又唔話報警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ce127037c3976c08a8d2098e55d1e1aa364e4e","tid":587447,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"泛民終終於識攪政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2ce86e8280c096b80f4739f979968c3947c059","tid":587447,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99d7d1c9111fdde41949d1401eacc65b244e624","tid":587447,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"係咪真係有咁多呀？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/210055_2760735506a5bc187a35f6c829fae70d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F210055_2760735506a5bc187a35f6c829fae70d.jpg&h=53c5be25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7909fb375c11664c703c0f549374e0ab2aee17a8","tid":587447,"uid":5489,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/ne